'''bullshit''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

#(''vulgar slang'') [[Deceitful]] statements; [[lie]]s; [[exaggeration]]; [[nonsense]].
#(''vulgar'') A card game in which the object is to bluff about cards laid down without one's opponents noticing and to determine when one's opponents are bluffing.

